div.div: The site so far has been written in Markdown. So you would want to edit the markdown file associated with the page you're interested in changing. This page can be found by clicking the `suggest an edit` button from the website, or cloning and finding the corresponding markdown page (which should be easy since they are all organized into directories based on topic). I recommend reading the pinned issue, which has some more information as well as the README.
